# Frontend Environment Configuration

# API URL - Optional, auto-detected if not set
# When not set, the frontend will automatically use the current hostname with port 8000
# This allows the app to work on any network without configuration
#
# For explicit configuration:
#   NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:8000/api/v1
#   NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://192.168.1.100:8000/api/v1
#   NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://api.yourdomain.com/api/v1
#
# Leave commented out for automatic detection (recommended for development)
# NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:8000/api/v1